author: HBO Max
description:
It’s the season finale of #ITWelcomeToDerry and this episode is full of incredible guests. Andy and Barbara Muschietti (Executive Producers) walk us through crafting an ending that’s cosmic, chaotic, and heartbreakingly beautiful. 

Then, the entire Losers Club (Arian S. Cartaya, Matilda Lawler, Amanda Christine, Clara Stack, and Blake James) joins the podcast to reflect on filming the finale, the bonds forged on set, and what their characters face in these final moments. Finally, Bill Skarsgård, joined by Andy Muschietti, steps in to break down his return as Pennywise, the evolution of the character, and the challenge of balancing terror, humor, and tragedy in his most unhinged scenes yet.
